name: Blanche_Modern_White_Molded_Plastic_Dining_Chairs_(Set_of_2)
reviews: I just bought 4 more after owning 2 for a few years. These are great chairs we use them indoors at the dining table where I have a mix of all white chairs.

I absolutley love the chais! I bought 4 of them, I live on the 6th floor which at times it can get very windy. The chair design and weight made this an excellent choice. I have never had to stack them or move them because of rain or wind. They are easy to whipe clean and maintain. I also love the modern design, I have put them around a glass top table with stainless steel legs. Oh, by the way they are very comfortable.
description:
These beautiful, minimalist Blanche dining chairs are an ideal choice for those looking to adopt a clean, contemporary look for their home. Made from a single mold, these modern stackable dining chairs are constructed of durable plastic.
